>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"recruit-corp-grid__item -col-6 -sp-col-6\">\r\n              <div class=\"recruit-corp-3min-item\">\r\n                <h3 class=\"recruit-corp-3min-item__ttl\">有給休暇取得率<br>2025年度</h3>\r\n                <div class=\"recruit-corp-3min-item__contents\">\r\n                  <div class=\"recruit-corp-3min-item__img\"><img src=\"/assets/img/recruit/corporate/3min/img_item12.svg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"></div>\r\n                  <div class=\"recruit-corp-3min-item__num\"><span>75.0</span>％</div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"recruit-corp-grid__item -col-6 -sp-col-6\">\r\n              <div class=\"recruit-corp-3min-item\">\r\n                <h3 class=\"recruit-corp-3min-item__ttl\">離職率<br>2025年度</h3>\r\n                <div class=\"recruit-corp-3min-item__contents\">\r\n                  <div class=\"recruit-corp-3min-item__img\"><img src=\"/assets/img/recruit/corporate/3min/img_item13.svg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"></div>\r\n                  <div class=\"recruit-corp-3min-item__num\"><span>4.8</span>％</div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"recruit-corp-grid__item -col-6 -sp-col-12\">\r\n              <div class=\"recruit-corp-3min-item\">\r\n                <h3 class=\"recruit-corp-3min-item__ttl\">正規雇用労働者の<br class=\"sp-tb:view\">中途採用比率</h3>\r\n                <div class=\"recruit-corp-3min-item__contents\">\r\n                  <dl class=\"recruit-corp-3min-item__list\">\r\n                    <div>\r\n                      <dt>2025年度</dt>\r\n                      <dd class=\"recruit-corp-3min-item__num\"><span>46</span>%</dd>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                      <dt>2024年度</dt>\r\n                      <dd class=\"recruit-corp-3min-item__num\"><span>55</span>%</dd>\r\n          